               <p>H. Sarjent. No; I did not.</p>
               <p>Q. What was his complaint?</p>
               <p>H. Sarjent. He was taken with a at first, he had a pain in his bowels and a cold, and a shivering in all his limbs.</p>
               <p>Q. Was he agueish?</p>
               <p>H. Sarjent. Yes; I should think so.</p>
