               <p>S. Sarjent. No.</p>
               <p>Q. Do you know what time she came home on Saturday night?</p>
               <p>S. Sarjent. She came home at twelve o'clock, I sat up for her.</p>
               <p>Q. What character does the prisoner bear?</p>
               <p>S. Sarjent. He bears the character of a very honest sober man.</p>
